---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="How We Work" description="Our process for delivering digital marketing results. From initial audit to ongoing optimisation, here's exactly what working with Spires Digital looks like.">
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'How We Work' }]} />

  <section class="page-hero" style="margin-top: -2rem;">
    <div class="container page-hero-content">
      <span class="badge">Our Process</span>
      <h1>How We Work With You</h1>
      <p>No mystery, no jargon. Here's exactly what happens when you partner with Spires Digital, from first contact to ongoing growth.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-num">1</span>
            <span class="timeline-label">Week 0</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h2>Free Audit & Discovery Call</h2>
            <p>We start with a thorough audit of your current marketing. We review your accounts, analytics, competitors, and market position. Then we jump on a call to discuss your goals, budget, and timeline.</p>
            <div class="timeline-detail">
              <h4>What you get:</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Comprehensive account audit report</li>
                <li>Competitor analysis summary</li>
                <li>Quick-win opportunities identified</li>
                <li>30-minute strategy call</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="tip-box"><strong>This is completely free.</strong> Even if you don't work with us, you'll walk away with actionable insights you can implement yourself.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-num">2</span>
            <span class="timeline-label">Week 1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h2>Strategy & Setup</h2>
            <p>Once you're on board, we build your custom strategy. This isn't a template -- it's a detailed plan based on your specific business, market, and goals.</p>
            <div class="timeline-detail">
              <h4>What happens:</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Campaign structure designed</li>
                <li>Conversion tracking audited or set up from scratch</li>
                <li>Audience research and keyword planning</li>
                <li>Creative briefs and ad copy drafting</li>
                <li>Full access to all accounts granted to you</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-num">3</span>
            <span class="timeline-label">Week 2-4</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h2>Launch & Initial Optimisation</h2>
            <p>Campaigns go live. The first few weeks are about gathering data, testing assumptions, and making rapid adjustments. We monitor performance daily during this phase.</p>
            <div class="timeline-detail">
              <h4>What you see:</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Campaigns launched across chosen channels</li>
                <li>Daily monitoring and bid adjustments</li>
                <li>A/B testing on ad copy and creative</li>
                <li>Weekly check-in to review early data</li>
                <li>Negative keyword refinement (PPC)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <span class="timeline-num">4</span>
            <span class="timeline-label">Monthly</span>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h2>Ongoing Optimisation & Reporting</h2>
            <p>This is where the real growth happens. Every month, we analyse performance, identify opportunities, and refine the strategy. You get a clear report and a strategy call.</p>
            <div class="timeline-detail">
              <h4>What's included:</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Monthly performance report in plain English</li>
                <li>Strategy call to review results and plan next steps</li>
                <li>Continuous campaign optimisation</li>
                <li>New keyword/audience expansion</li>
                <li>Budget reallocation based on what's working</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="badge">Our Commitment</span>
        <h2>What You Can Always Expect</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="promise-card">
          <h3>Full Transparency</h3>
          <p>You own every account. You see every metric. You know exactly where every penny goes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-card">
          <h3>No Lock-In</h3>
          <p>Month-to-month agreements. If we're not delivering, you're free to leave with 30 days notice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-card">
          <h3>Real Communication</h3>
          <p>No jargon-filled reports. We explain what's working, what isn't, and what we're doing about it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-card">
          <h3>Data-Driven</h3>
          <p>Every decision is backed by data. We test, measure, and let the numbers guide the strategy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-card">
          <h3>Fast Response</h3>
          <p>Questions answered within 24 hours. Urgent issues addressed same day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-card">
          <h3>Results Focus</h3>
          <p>We optimise for business outcomes -- revenue, leads, profit -- not vanity metrics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p>The first step is a free, no-obligation audit. We'll show you exactly where the opportunities are.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Get Your Free Audit</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .process-timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 3rem; }

  .process-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 17px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  .timeline-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .timeline-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .timeline-num {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .timeline-content h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .timeline-content > p { color: var(--color-text-light); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

  .timeline-detail {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .timeline-detail h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-detail ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .timeline-detail li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  .timeline-detail li::before {
    content: '\2713';
    color: var(--color-success);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .promise-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .promise-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .promise-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-timeline { padding-left: 2.5rem; }
    .timeline-marker { left: -2.5rem; }
  }
</style>
